    "This task aims to aid in understanding the dynamics behind how different politicians employ lifestyles in their self-descriptions.",
    "This task takes advantage of LLM's ability to recognize words when guided with a direct prompt.",
    "We refer to this type of researcher-guided task as a specific use case that is supervised on account of the directed instructions provided to the model.",
    "The second example uses ChatGPT to uncover themes or topics in text excerpts from etiquette books.",
    "The texts were selected because they mention smoking and the research aims to inductively examine social norms around smoking and their change over time."
